    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Assuming you want the part between single quotes, use this regular expression with a <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/Matcher.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>Matcher</code></a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>\"'(.*?)'\"\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String mydata = \"some string with 'the data i want' inside\";\nPattern pattern = Pattern.compile(\"'(.*?)'\");\nMatcher matcher = pattern.matcher(mydata);\nif (matcher.find())\n{\n    System.out.println(matcher.group(1));\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Result:</p>\n\n<pre>\nthe data i want\n</pre>\n"
  }, {
