    "question_id" : 4662215,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>There's a simple one-liner for this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String target = myData.replaceAll(\"[^']*(?:'(.*?)')?.*\", \"$1\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>By making the matching group optional, this also caters for quotes not being found by returning a blank in that case.</p>\n\n<p>See <a href=\"http://ideone.com/f1Ann2\" rel=\"noreferrer\">live demo</a>.</p>\n"
  }, {
