    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>add <strong>apache.commons</strong> dependency on your <strong>pom.xml</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.commons&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;commons-io&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;1.3.2&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And below code works.</p>\n\n<pre><code>StringUtils.substringBetween(String mydata, String \"'\", String \"'\")\n</code></pre>\n"
