    "question_id" : 4662215,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Some how the group(1) didnt work for me. I used group(0) to find the url version.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Pattern urlVersionPattern = Pattern.compile(\"\\\\/v[0-9][a-z]{0,1}\\\\/\");\nMatcher m = urlVersionPattern.matcher(url);\nif (m.find()) { \n    return StringUtils.substringBetween(m.group(0), \"/\", \"/\");\n}\nreturn \"v0\";\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4647011,
      "reputation" : 45022,
      "user_id" : 3764965,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 94,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/7O3Pe.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Nikolas",
