  "body" : "<p>I have a string that has two single quotes in it, the <code>'</code> character. In between the single quotes is the data I want.</p>\n\n<p>How can I write a regex to extract \"the data i want\" from the following text?</p>\n\n<pre><code>mydata = \"some string with 'the data i want' inside\";\n</code></pre>\n"
